**Story**

Once upon a time, In a forest there lived a monkey near the banks of the river. 
In the same foresst there lived Mr. crocodile and his wife, Mrs. Crocodile.
One day the crocodile was resting under the tree near the banks of the river, the kind-hearted monkey offered him some fruits.
The crocodile came back again for more fruits and they both became good friends!
the monkey gave fruits for the crocodile's wife,and she ate the fruits and adored them and was also jealous as she did not like her husband spend more time withe the monkey.
then one fine day she told her husband that if the fruits were so juicy i wonder how sweet the monkeys heart would be, so get me the heart of the monkey!
the crocodile was not willing to kill his freind but had no ption but rather to obey his wife!